// Windows Application Icon resource for Y2Kmeter_Standalone
//   - Linked separately into Y2Kmeter_Standalone target (Windows only),
//     coexisting with JUCE-generated Y2Kmeter_resources.rc (VERSION_INFO).
//   - Resource ID 1 is what Windows Explorer prefers for EXE file icon.
//   - Icon path is relative to this .rc file location (assets/).
//
// Note: rc.exe accepts C-style comments.

1 ICON "icon.ico"
